These are Puzzles for 2x3 Level 3

.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-3-1::.
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: documentary, superhero, musical
The people use 3 different means of transport: quad-bike, scooter, tram
1. the person watching documentary movies is the person driving the scooter##1
2. the person driving the tram is on the right of the person driving the scooter##1
3. the person driving the tram is on the left or right of the person watching superhero movies##3
4. the person driving the scooter is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |     3      |
| Movie-Genre   | documentary | musical | superhero    |
| Transport     | scooter    | tram       | quad-bike |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-3-2::.
The people have 3 different jobs:  manager, accountant, mechanic
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: cricket, snowboarding, skiing
1. the person who's sport is cricket is on the left of the person who's sport is snowboarding##1
2. the mechanic is on the left of the manager##1
3. the person who's sport is cricket is on the far left or far right##3
4. the accountant is the person who's sport is skiing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1   |     2     |     3      |
| Job     | mechanic | manager | accountant  |
| Sport   | cricket  | snowboarding  | skiing |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-3-3::.
The people have 3 different jobs:  scientist, architect, writer
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: gospel, trance, hip-hop
1. the fan of trance is on the far left or far right##3
2. the scientist is on the far right##1
3. the architect is the fan of hip-hop##1
4. the fan of trance is on the right of the fan of hip-hop##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |     2     |     3      |
| Job           | writer | architect | scientist |
| Music-Genre   | gospel        | hip-hop    | trance        |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-3-4::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: traveling, gardening, camping
3 different pets are kept: rabbit, pony, hedgehog
1. the person who's hobby is camping is on the left of the person who's hobby is gardening##1
2. the person who's hobby is camping is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is gardening##3
3. the owner of the rabbit is between the person who's hobby is camping and the owner of the hedgehog##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |    2    |   3    |
| Hobby   | camping | gardening | traveling |
| Pet     | pony  | rabbit    | hedgehog  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-3-5::.
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: adventure, drama, mystery
The people use 3 different means of transport: bike, van, boat
1. the person driving the boat is on the left or right of the person watching adventure movies##3
2. the person driving the van is on the left of the person driving the bike##1
3. the person driving the boat is on the right of the person watching adventure movies##1
4. the person watching adventure movies is between the person watching drama movies and the person driving the boat##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |   2    |   3    |
| Movie-Genre   | drama | adventure | mystery |
| Transport     | van   | bike   | boat   |

