.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-3-6::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: woodworking, camping, board-games
The people have 3 different jobs:  librarian, police-officer, doctor
1. the doctor is on the left of the librarian##1
2. the person who's hobby is camping is on the right of the person who's hobby is woodworking##1
3. the person who's hobby is board-games is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is woodworking##3
4. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the right of the police-officer##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |   2    |     3      |
| Hobby   | board-games | woodworking | camping      |
| Job     | police-officer  | doctor | librarian |

