.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-3-7::.
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: soul, house, trance
There are 3 different nationalities: thai, japanese, german
1. the fan of trance is on the right of the japanese##1
2. the german is on the left of the fan of soul##1
3. the german is on the left or right of the fan of house##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |     2     |     3      |
| Music-Genre   | house  | trance    | soul       |
| Nationality   | japanese | german | thai |

