.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-3-8::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: 7up, iced-tea, coffee
There 3 different types of food: kale, mango, grapefruit
1. the person drinking 7up is the person eating kale##1
2. the person eating mango is in the middle##1
3. the person drinking coffee is on the left of the person drinking iced-tea##1
4. the person drinking iced-tea is on the left or right of the person eating kale##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |   2    |   3    |
| Beverage   | coffee        | iced-tea  | 7up   |
| Food       | grapefruit | mango | kale |

