.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-3-12::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: lemonade, hot-chocolate, fanta
There are 3 different nationalities: argentine, turkish, pakistani
1. the argentine is between the person drinking lemonade and the person drinking hot-chocolate##2
2. the turkish is the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
3. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the left of the person drinking fanta##1
4. the argentine is on the left or right of the person drinking lemonade##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2     |    3    |
| Beverage      | hot-chocolate    | fanta    | lemonade  |
| Nationality   | turkish | argentine | pakistani |

