.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-3-13::.
There are 3 different nationalities: indian, chinese, russian
3 different pets are kept: guinea-pig, hamster, snake
1. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the far left or far right##3
2. the russian is on the right of the owner of the hamster##1
3. the owner of the snake is between the owner of the hamster and the owner of the guinea-pig##2
4. the owner of the guinea-pig is the chinese##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |     3     |
| Nationality   | indian | russian | chinese |
| Pet           | hamster    | snake    | guinea-pig       |

