1. the fan of folk is in the middle##1
2. the person watching musical movies is between the fan of r&b and the fan of d&b##2
3. the fan of folk is on the right of the fan of d&b##1
4. the fan of r&b is the person watching scientific movies##1
5. the fan of d&b is on the left or right of the person watching musical movies##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |   2    |     3     |
| Movie-Genre   | romance | musical | scientific |
| Music-Genre   | d&b     | folk  | r&b    |

