.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-3-20::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: iced-tea, fanta, almond-milk
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: family, satire, disaster
1. the person watching satire movies is on the left or right of the person drinking almond-milk##3
2. the person drinking fanta is on the left of the person watching family movies##1
3. the person drinking iced-tea is on the right of the person watching satire movies##1
4. the person watching disaster movies is on the left of the person drinking fanta##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |       2       |      3      |
| Beverage      | almond-milk    | fanta | iced-tea         |
| Movie-Genre   | disaster | satire  | family |

 